{"tid":83571,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友覺得我好污糟好假⋯","createTime":"2017-01-16T23:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T12:51:22.000Z","uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e64f4258fb486f9411cc35d5a170d3c3255de7c","tid":83571,"uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T23:44:46.000Z","msg":"係完全唔情願嘅情況下⋯有推開對方⋯<br />\n隻豬仲係度 但被人嘗試搞過⋯ <br />\n男朋友話覺得我好污糟⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但成件事係我唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n仲有佢話以為我好乖 <br />\n但估唔到我會同男仔（ex)係外面過夜⋯ (我仲細⋯1x歲）<br />\n好亂呀好複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以點 <br />\n好想死 佢要分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話唔識再面對我<br />\n佢淨係會同乖乖女拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話覺得我呃咗佢咁<br />\n同佢嘅期望有太大落差⋯<br />\n我再講任何野佢都已經唔信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：拍咗幾個月 用咗好大勇氣先敢同佢講<br />\n佢係處"},{"pid":"1c7d00645d09a5e70251730b917f516cb4ad0509","tid":83571,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T23:45:58.000Z","msg":"飛咗佢啦 咁小事嫌三嫌四"},{"pid":"a80